bullets: The following models are now deprecated in GitHub Models. Please transition to the suggested versions to continue using the improved models with enhanced features:
Mistral-Nemo users should transition to Mistral-small-2503 .
Mistral-large-2411 users should transition to Mistral-medium-2505 .
Also, Jais-30b-chat is no longer available in GitHub Models.
To learn more about GitHub Models, check out the docs . You can also join our community discussions .
